    SDL_Surface *screen = SDL_GetWindowSurface(window);
    SDL_SetSurfaceBlendMode(screen, SDL_BLENDMODE_BLEND);

    // Load images (later)
    // ...

    // Main loop
    while (...) {
        // Handle events, update game state, and render frames
    }

    SDL_Quit();
    return 0;
}
```
**Allegro Example:**
```c
